{"tid":586804,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"個女仔係咪中意我？","createTime":"2018-03-10T01:06:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-10T07:49:54.000Z","uid":96435,"like":4,"dislike":68,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"ff697ca9fa2777e9562724e19e06314cf92f9f5f","tid":586804,"uid":96435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T01:06:11.000Z","msg":"識咗十年 中意咗兩年 追咗一年<br />\n個女仔乖乖女嚟 冇拍過拖 平時唔太出聲 出街齋試衫唔買衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n開頭追只係靠每日whatsapp傾計<br />\n因為大家都有野忙 所以冇乜點面對面傾計<br />\n追咗三個月就表咗白 佢初頭好抗拒但我之後日日送佢中意食嘅朱古力比佢 佢都有講多謝<br />\n去到近呢一個月因為某啲原因日日見 開始會面對面傾計 但我同佢講野 佢唔敢望我 但講好多野 有次特登lecture坐佢隔離 點知佢執野走 我灰咗下冇執野咁去咗廁所 返嚟又見佢坐返我隔離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n明顯咁feel到whatsapp錄音個語氣同平時講野唔一樣 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁姐係我得咗？<br />\n至於我就 冇拍過拖 亦都唔知有冇人中意過自己 冇經歷過比人中意 中學做過兵之後脫咗毒 社交能力算係高 成日氹老人家同毒撚frd笑 算係乖乖仔 男女frd比例 6:4 <br />\n唯獨有啲大男人 想提升自己等未來伴侶可以唔洗做野 做自己興趣同湊小朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc3b4e3c5f442407081f070135303a5cbf06a66b","tid":586804,"uid":71226,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T01:07:38.000Z","msg":"你都係想我講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係啊去馬啦</span>"},{"pid":"e0d6ab30f92280903b700f844d213cef83b85132","tid":586804,"uid":96435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fc3b4e3c5f442407081f070135303a5cbf06a66b","tid":586804,"uid":71226,"like":24,"dislike":1,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T01:07:38.000Z","msg":"你都係想我講<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係啊去馬啦</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T01:09:07.000Z","msg":"唔確定係咪畀人frd zone咗定兵咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n始終做過兵 有啲驚"},{"pid":"5411dcd500ecef3e72354cc1e0fd3b16bda3fe11","tid":586804,"uid":154554,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T01:10:46.000Z","msg":"人生三大錯覺"},{"pid":"6664b7fc1d7ee9ba92da53cbcd9c5138c15206cd","tid":586804,"uid":8726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T01:12:22.000Z","msg":"信自己啦<br />\n女仔鍾意你 你實會feel到"},{"pid":"1ed6cd6fe63fafd5ef60c2ef79074c508c671112","tid":586804,"uid":96435,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6664b7fc1d7ee9ba92da53cbcd9c5138c15206cd","tid":586804,"uid":8726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T01:12:22.000Z","msg":"信自己啦<br />\n女仔鍾意你 你實會feel到"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T01:13:46.000Z","msg":"其實係feel到嘅 不過驚feel錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"510c10a0b20b5a21b46da2c197c33995c390f7d7","tid":586804,"uid":96435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1ed6cd6fe63fafd5ef60c2ef79074c508c671112","tid":586804,"uid":96435,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6664b7fc1d7ee9ba92da53cbcd9c5138c15206cd","tid":586804,"uid":8726,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T01:12:22.000Z","msg":"信自己啦<br />\n女仔鍾意你 你實會feel到"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T01:13:46.000Z","msg":"其實係feel到嘅 不過驚feel錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T01:15:14.000Z","msg":"同埋唔知嗰種感覺"},{"pid":"510249d5db2615ab09347b722b540451f82f1e22","tid":586804,"uid":29093,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T01:17:17.000Z","msg":"笑左， 你未講埋你第日想做咩職業 買樓買邊區 同埋婚禮葬禮點搞"},{"pid":"b2c76af545c6bb15aa58eecaec782c421ac90ed1","tid":586804,"uid":92065,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-10T01:18:28.000Z","msg":"怕咩？你都表過一次白啦<br />\n就算係get咪當瘀多次姐"},{"pid":"4ddd91bd7aefe62cfd5edf0b27406707a485c210","tid":586804,"uid":96435,"l